    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for a general overview. To make it more engaging for my students, could you add some specific, landmark Supreme Court cases that really highlight this protection of rights? I want them to see how this actually works in practice to safeguard people's freedoms.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
